Sokolovska Uhelna and Dalkia CR
would be interested in  CEZ (CEZ)  AS power plants that may be for sale
as part of the settlement with the European Commission,
 Hospodarske Noviny  reported, citing executives of the companies.  Sokolovska Uhelna, a brown coal supplier to CEZ AS, would
probably be interested in acquiring the Tisova plant from CEZ,
the newspaper reported, citing Chief Executive Officer Frantisek Stepanek.  Dalkia CR would look at purchasing CEZ Detmarovice plant,
 Hospodarske Noviny , said citing Chairman Zdenek Duba.  CEZ AS hasnâ€™t decided yet what plants it will sell under a
settlement with the European Commission, the newspaper added.  To contact the reporter on this story:
